OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FAndy Burnham's plan for a "No 10 in
OL,7,Fthe North" is an "important gesture in
OL,8,Fthe right direction", leading
OL,9,Fdevolution proponent Lord Heseltine
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe Tory grandee, who was the first to
OL,13,Fcall for directly elected mayors in
OL,14,F1991, said it could be "very
OL,15,Fbeneficial" to "our entire economy" if
OL,16,Fthe presumptive next prime minister
OL,17,Fdelivered on the broad vision he set
OL,18,Fout on Monday.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@JO]oD@ROUpD@TO]vD@XOUwD@KO]wD@
OL,26,APOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FHe described the former Greater
OL,7,FManchester mayor as "the manifestation
OL,8,Fof the dream" behind work by the
OL,9,FConservatives under Lord Cameron,
OL,10,Ftogether with Labour, to push power
OL,11,Fout of Whitehall.
OL,13,FMr Burnham, who looks set to enter
OL,14,FDowning Street within weeks, used a
OL,15,Fspeech on Monday to pledge to "rewire"
OL,16,Fthe British state with greater
OL,17,Fdecision-making handed to local
OL,18,Fleaders.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@MO]wD@_OUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FHis flagship proposal was the creation
OL,7,Fof an outpost of 10 Downing Street
OL,8,Fbased in Manchester, which would serve
OL,9,Fas the "nerve centre" through which to
OL,10,Fdeliver priorities including
OL,11,Freindustrialisation and redistributing
OL,12,Fpower across the UK.
OL,14,FThe plan also got the backing of
OL,15,FHousing Secretary Steve Reed, who said
OL,16,Fit was a "great idea" as he threw his
OL,17,Fweight behind the Makerfield MP's
OL,18,Fpledge to "go further and faster" on
OL,19,Fdevolution.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@UO]xD@JOUxD@UO]zD@KOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FMr Reed said Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,7,FGovernment had "made a fantastic
OL,8,Fstart, but Andy has made clear he
OL,9,Fwants to go further and faster, and I
OL,10,Ffully support that".
OL,12,FLord Heseltine backed the proposal of
OL,13,Fa "No 10 in the North", but suggested
OL,14,Fthat focusing the unit on
OL,15,Fdecentralisation would matter more
OL,16,Fthan its location.
OL,26,@oD@POUrD@SO]uD@COUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FAsked about the plans in an interview
OL,7,Fwith the Press Association, he said:
OL,8,F"The critical thing is to have a Prime
OL,9,FMinister who is committed to the
OL,10,Fdevolution agenda, and without that,
OL,11,Fthe various components of power in
OL,12,FWhitehall will fragment and resist.
OL,14,F"Creating a powerful No 10 unit,
OL,15,Fwhether it's in Manchester or in
OL,16,FLondon or anywhere else, is an
OL,17,Fimportant gesture in the right
OL,18,Fdirection."
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FHe described Manchester as "probably
OL,7,Fthe most effective example of what
OL,8,FDavid Cameron began to introduce" with
OL,9,Fdevolution reforms under the
OL,10,Fstewardship of then-communities
OL,11,Fsecretary Greg Clark.
OL,13,F"Andy is the present manifestation of
OL,14,Fthe dream that people like me had when
OL,15,Fwe started the journey to devolution,"
OL,16,Fthe former Tory deputy prime minister
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@\OUpD@aO]uD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FBut he warned against proposals to
OL,7,Fhand local leaders the power to set
OL,8,Fand retain business rates in their
OL,9,Farea, which Mr Burnham has reportedly
OL,10,Fbeen advised to consider, arguing that
OL,11,Fdifferences in revenue at a local
OL,12,Flevel must be balanced out by some
OL,13,Fintervention from central Government.
OL,15,F"If I was advising Andy Burnham now
OL,16,FI'd say look, don't tinker around with
OL,17,Flocal income tax or local rates, get
OL,18,Fon with the job of generating wealth,
OL,19,Fand that is basically using capital
OL,20,Ffunds," he said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FLord Heseltine, who in 2012 authored a
OL,7,Fmajor report that served as the
OL,8,Fblueprint for devolution policies
OL,9,Fpursued by Lord Cameron's government,
OL,10,Fsaid he had a "very good relationship"
OL,11,Fwith Mr Burnham in his former role as
OL,12,Fmetro mayor.
OL,14,F"It's very important, and Andy
OL,15,FBurnham, I thought, made a very
OL,16,Fsensible remark when he said he's
OL,17,Fgoing to reach out across the
OL,18,Fpolitical divide," he said.
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@fO]vD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FAsked about the tone of Mr Burnham's
OL,7,Fspeech more broadly, Lord Heseltine
OL,8,Fsaid: "I thought the message was
OL,9,Faccurate. Tell the truth, don't get
OL,10,Finvolved in committing what you can't
OL,11,Fdeliver, and recognise we're all in
OL,12,Fthis together.
OL,14,F"This is not a public or private
OL,15,Fsector monopoly, it is mobilising and
OL,16,Fenthusing people up and down the power
OL,17,Fstructure, and that means you have to
OL,18,Ftake a broad view, and I thought that
OL,19,FAndy Burnham expressed that clearly."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FHe added: "Certainly to me, I've been
OL,7,Finvolved in this devolution agenda all
OL,8,Fmy political life, what he was saying
OL,9,Fmade sense, and if he now carries it
OL,10,Fthrough with determination, we could
OL,11,Ffind a very beneficial consequence for
OL,12,Fall our political parties, and our
OL,13,Fentire economy."
OL,15,FDespite welcoming the prospect of
OL,16,Fcross-party cooperation, Lord
OL,17,FHeseltine said he believed Labour and
OL,18,Fthe Tories should both work to
OL,19,F"expose" Reform UK, which he describes
OL,20,Fas an "extremist" proposition.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@PO]{D@AOU{D@HO]|D@GOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FAnd he welcomed Mr Burnham's
OL,7,FMakerfield by-election victory as "a
OL,8,Fvery substantial advantage for those
OL,9,Fof us who believe in the dangers of
OL,10,FReform."
OL,12,F"Nigel Farage set out to appear as
OL,13,F(Donald) Trump's vicar in Britain but
OL,14,Fis now more likely to be seen as his
OL,15,Frelic," he said.
OL,26,@oD@cOUrD@HO]tD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782865086
OL,3,CTory grandee Michael Heseltine backs
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's No 10 North
OL,6,FA Reform UK spokesperson said: 'This
OL,7,Fis the same old tired, establishment
OL,8,Fsmear we've heard for years from out-
OL,9,Fof-touch grandees like Lord Heseltine.
OL,10,FIf Labour and the Conservatives want
OL,11,Fto form an alliance, good luck to
OL,12,Fthem.'
OL,14,FMr Reed, seen so far as an arch
OL,15,FStarmer loyalist, said he hoped Mr
OL,16,FBurnham would be installed in No 10
OL,17,F"as quickly as possible" by the end of
OL,18,FJuly as he enjoyed "very widespread
OL,19,Fsupport amongst the Parliamentary
OL,20,FLabour Party".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@XO]zD@TOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
